. 
. di ""


. di as res "All age-combined per-product CSVVs written to `CSVVDIR'"
All age-combined per-product CSVVs written to /user/ab5405/summeraliaclimate/co
> de/regressions/output/age_combined_csvv_ALLREA

. 
end of do-file
